{"tid":1298291,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣通過request url redirect 去指定既port?","createTime":"2019-07-08T23:58:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T13:12:44.000Z","uid":181941,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5775f6109be8f47829df5a24c1a4c8464e667f0e","tid":1298291,"uid":181941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T23:58:25.000Z","msg":"細佬屋企個server有幾個web service host緊, 一直都係用 <code>domain_name:port</code>去access<br />\n想問點先做到打<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">domain_name/webservice_a</code></pre><br />\n會幫我redirect到指定既port?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99944173002982dd6b32af9d46414c963be8e96b","tid":1298291,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T23:59:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb9945d5741e46eb7d830c0ba9e3c79c857723d","tid":1298291,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:13:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/27997071/redirecting-from-port-80-to-different-ports-based-on-url\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstackoverflow.com%2Fquestions%2F27997071%2Fredirecting-from-port-80-to-different-ports-based-on-url&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0duDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=3d7928f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://stackoverflow.com/questions/27997071/redirecting-from-port-80-to-different-ports-based-on-url</a>"},{"pid":"34376e42177b5d62a55d163e5b711735fc511423","tid":1298291,"uid":125976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5775f6109be8f47829df5a24c1a4c8464e667f0e","tid":1298291,"uid":181941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T23:58:25.000Z","msg":"細佬屋企個server有幾個web service host緊, 一直都係用 <code>domain_name:port</code>去access<br />\n想問點先做到打<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">domain_name/webservice_a</code></pre><br />\n會幫我redirect到指定既port?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:20:22.000Z","msg":"Reverse Proxy 都唔識就搞 webhost<br />\n<br />\n睇嚟可以一齊燒炭<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c203dd3295798e17309415ac28011ae0388e7dbb","tid":1298291,"uid":116953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:40:26.000Z","msg":"唔講用咩host<br />\n當正常用nginx<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">server{\n    listen 80;\n    server_name domain.com;\n    location ~/webserivce_a/ {\n        proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:8080;\n        proxy_set_header X-Real-IP  $remote_addr;\n        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $remote_addr;\n        proxy_set_header Host $host;\n    }\n}</code></pre><br />\n如果用docker可以再簡單D"},{"pid":"38a3054811be8ab7bdbd490ef6ef75fb1af70c90","tid":1298291,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:52:07.000Z","msg":"nginx 完"},{"pid":"771d9781e4ba0bd3bb37cc54a665e8bd49e77c83","tid":1298291,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:46:41.000Z","msg":"直接唔得，間接就⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://domain.com/web1/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdomain.com%2Fweb1%2Findex.html&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0duDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=c87763ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://domain.com/web1/index.html</a><br />\n內裡做HTML redirect去 <a href=\"http://domain.com:8001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdomain.com%3A8001&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0duDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=19331624\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://domain.com:8001</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://domain.com/web2/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdomain.com%2Fweb2%2Findex.html&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0duDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=4c72f63a\"